{"tid":484760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由幾時開始，報警變左信用基礎？","createTime":"2017-11-30T11:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T11:39:05.000Z","uid":46849,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97416b46600dd4fbc1fa9a0bfa5dfba36276034f","tid":484760,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:02:58.000Z","msg":"警察？認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6221379bd7d218b90b8783ffbe21ea08ed1bb96f","tid":484760,"uid":60164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警察？認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同未成年少女發生性行為刑事罪黎<br />\n點解唔報警"},{"pid":"7567e6e4b54944727923d6a7b076b7ce31c152c2","tid":484760,"uid":139139,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警察？認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢做乜野都證明唔到個教練搞鳩佢，乜嘢勇敢企出嚟，只係可以睇得出香港人鍾意睇嘅係故事，而唔係香港核心價值之一 法律公正。冇證冇據講乜嘢都冇用，好可惜位喺度德高地嘅人太多，教練咁就比人哋搞到冇咗份工。<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講乜嘢細路女好驚，唔識比反應。大佬佢係中學生，唔係細路女，16歲已經可以自己決定好多野，人哋除佢條底褲嘅時候唔識反抗？唔識掙扎？你落去搵個小學生都識啦！<br />\n<br />\n俾人搞完，之後仲未反應到？唔識同屋企人講？唔識同學校社工講？要等到八年之後冇證冇據先開片？<br />\n<br />\n仲要同人地一齊過生日？會唔會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0471000cd8eba9c4910ca71477abb49ba023ab1","tid":484760,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6624a138f804805347820f5583bb779a5e2668d8","tid":484760,"uid":30563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"刑事案唔報警咁你目的係咩呀？"},{"pid":"220bc7a037f9931dbe9dbc4f899e6c8a8853825b","tid":484760,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:39:05.000Z","msg":"刑事不如自己解決啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgm